Seriously, Alot of great long time pker's joined team newt BECAUSE they would have more targets.<br>
The newts are fantastic pker's and they did have to fight goods from the start, that gave some of them a leg up on pk's. They were always going to win in points. The druid factor and tracking factor always downplayed by team newt was a huge boon to them as we still don't have enough shaman, or wizards or bards over 35. Druids had the qualities of all three of these classes and were pking for points from day one. <br>
I also agree about the evil pking especially before all the big negative points days. Im sure evil was getting negative points for weeks before it really started to show,after all we did level faster. <br>
<br>
