I have alot and it was not worth it. We would make it to a big zone after alot of travel and organizing. Now usually the first ganking would be easy, most pking is surprise ganking.<br>
The next fights we would encounter wold be more even and ill tell you alot of those early even battles were won.<br>
Ok heres the big part. After the first initial battle if the wizards did not evac out(and basically we fought alot of the time below level 29) things would get real messy with 4 zones of people tracking you down. The newts were viscious if they caught ya, corpse camping swearinf just plain nasty.<br>
I have fought various good guilds of same OR higher level and they were way more honorable.<br>
Ok even the times we did get away the pk day was over as its too hard to keep a well balanced team together that has to evac after every gimp kill because of the whole tracking non tracking issue. Shoot, half the time i made pk runs without sow!<br>
<br>
Now factor in that all it takes for a descent newt pk team is two people, a druid and anyoe else and you see why team newt wqas set up for points kills from the beginning.<br>
<br>
Oh well, at least lepin really knows the story from both sides.<br>
He's the only one i believe.<br>
i don't mind newts gettin alot of points and shouting about it, just shut up about the underdog part of it cause its all bullshit.<br>
